{"tid":576151,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"重覆犯錯 只有我在原地踏步","createTime":"2018-02-28T16:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T17:24:26.000Z","uid":40593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2144f08478d78cdd7b9e397b2c540d83dcf8245d","tid":576151,"uid":40593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲好似我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n肥妹為人獨家村、毒L性格<br />\n<br />\n我係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拍過幾次拖都唔識吸取教訓，個世界圍著另一半轉，每次有男朋友就忽略咗啲朋友，少咗同佢地聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經唔太識同朋友相處了<br />\n<br />\n而且另一半都需要有私人時間，去娛樂去social, 玩緊social緊邊到有時間陪我覆我機，成個世界圍住佢來轉，好容易因爲佢少咗時間分俾我而唔開心，又發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我都唔想架，每次發完都會後悔，係自己無朋友無興趣而過份緊張佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無論係另一半定舊老友都move on緊，都會認識新朋友新圈子，係我獨家村性格，只當中學時期玩開既做朋友，無論係大學或公司識既，我都只當係普通同學同事，當過客咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 係佢地正常係我自己仲原地踏步緊</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 係自己一直推走啲朋友，抵我做一世孤獨精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"09b6d883870a5ab4351490f491cd92d98706bb1b","tid":576151,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:09:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0787e21a2e10c02b22b10c316490086d91c2e2c","tid":576151,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09b6d883870a5ab4351490f491cd92d98706bb1b","tid":576151,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:09:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:10:53.000Z","msg":"你同條仔分咗手?"},{"pid":"dc02924b508321eb2cb83c5daa9da13e7238bc8b","tid":576151,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:11:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":